                                    ‡∏¢‡∏±‡∏á‡πÑ‡∏°‡πà‡∏°‡∏µ‡∏õ‡∏£‡∏∞‡∏ß‡∏±‡∏ï‡∏¥‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏£‡∏à‡∏±‡∏î‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏£‡∏™‡∏ï‡πá‡∏≠‡∏Å
                                </td>
                            </tr>
                            @endforelse
                        </tbody>
                    </table>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Add Stock Modal -->
    @if($showAddStockModal)
    <div class="fixed inset-0 bg-black bg-opacity-50 flex items-center justify-center p-4 z-50">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 w-full max-w-md">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-4">‡πÄ‡∏û‡∏¥‡πà‡∏°‡∏™‡∏ï‡πá‡∏≠‡∏Å‡∏™‡∏¥‡∏ô‡∏Ñ‡πâ‡∏≤</h3>
            
            <div class="space-y-4">
                <x-global.form-input
                    label="‡∏à‡∏≥‡∏ô‡∏ß‡∏ô‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πà‡∏ï‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏á‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏£‡πÄ‡∏û‡∏¥‡πà‡∏°"
                    type="number"
